{
  "stem": "20616.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I think to this date, the diamond industry is still run by that-- that clique.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then I joined the ranks of the unemployed for a while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I-- while I was in the service, I liberated a camera.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You know, when you first moved into Neustadt, all of the local population had to give up all binoculars and cameras.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Of course, the officers had first pick of the cameras.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They got all the good ones and were-- we were left with the little box cameras and the cheapies.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there was one camera that I remembered, which was a roller cord, which looked like a box camera and the officers didn't want.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I took that one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I got the local photographer in town to teach me how to use it and he developed the films and he gave me some pointers.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And as a child, I was always-- I once-- I did my own developing and everything.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "As a child, already I had a-- sort of a box camera, took pictures.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And-- and once there was an ad in the somebody was wanted-- an amateur photographer wanted who had floodlights, a tripod, and-- and a reflex camera, and a car.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "The only thing I had is a-- a reflex camera.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[SIGHS] That might be something for Elaine to-- [LAUGHS] of interest.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so I answered that ad and it was in Brooklyn.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They interviewed me and they said, yes, we can use any one who knows how to use that camera but you have to have a car and you have to have lights.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But we can help you out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We can get the lights for you, we can get a tripod for you.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
